WEBVTT

00:00:06.555 --> 00:00:09.173
Misteriji kolokvijalnog jezika

00:00:09.173 --> 00:00:10.816
Robot,

00:00:10.816 --> 00:00:12.898
stroj sposoban izvršavati

00:00:12.898 --> 00:00:15.793
programirane nizove radnji.

00:00:16.163 --> 00:00:18.325
Podrijetlo riječi robot

00:00:18.325 --> 00:00:20.678
datira od prije više od tisuću godina,

00:00:20.678 --> 00:00:23.879
iz doba kmetstva u središnjoj Europi,

00:00:23.879 --> 00:00:27.218
kad je služinstvo bilo sredstvo plaćanja.

00:00:27.218 --> 00:00:28.234
U to vrijeme,

00:00:28.234 --> 00:00:31.165
staroslavenska riječ rabota